Legend:
- istiod = Istio control plane (minimal profile)
- istio-ingressgateway = ingress gateway Service (NodePort: 30080/30443)
- istio-injection=enabled = namespace label for automatic Envoy sidecars
- otel-collector = OpenTelemetry Collector (OTLP gRPC 4317 / HTTP 4318)
- Traffic path: Host → Ingress → Gateway/VS → Service → Pod(+sidecar)
- Telemetry path: Envoy sidecar → OTLP → OTel Collector (logging exporter for now)
